window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Transform any space into a place of peace and calm with this inspiring guide from celebrated Zen master Thich Nhat Hanh. </p> <p>Designed for those new to mindfulness practices, <i>Making Space</i> offers easy-to-follow instructions for setting up a breathing room; listening to a bell; performing sitting, breathing, and walking meditations; and cooking and eating. Whether you live alone or with a family, this beautifully created audiobook can help you create a sense of retreat and sanctuary anywhere at home. </p>"; 
